&lt;p>This video is a philosophical monologue exploring the practical methods and mindset required to effectively engage in the process of asking &amp;ldquo;why.&amp;rdquo; The speaker treats &amp;ldquo;why&amp;rdquo; as a verb—an active inquiry—and moves beyond the simple advice to be curious, focusing instead on &lt;em>how&lt;/em> to balance questioning with action, patience, and self-awareness.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>What is Worth Saying?</title><link>https://cognware.com/posts/saas/whats-worth-saying/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 Aug 2025 08:19:27 +0530</pubDate><author>raj@cognware.com (CognWare Industries)</author><guid>https://cognware.com/posts/saas/whats-worth-saying/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group">SaaSx10
